data.text:
Proxima (formerly known as Team Proxima and Proxima Nova) is a mega-collaboration server known for creating levels such as Epsilon, Centauri, Polaris, Arcturus, Omicron, Acropolaris, Betelgeuse, and Scorpius. It was created in January 2018 by Splash and has over 1700 members, around 250 of whom are certified. It remained as a private, invite-only server until November 2020 when it was opened to the public.

In order to participate in megacollabs, members must apply for certification and be accepted by the majority of the admin team. Other events, such as contests, are open to all members of the server.

Levels[]

Insane Levels[]

Centauri (epic) by Tribar, HollowEarth, Firs, Belonzik, Reunomi, Splash, Lazuli, Maelstrom, Xender Game and Firs.

Demon Levels[]

Hard Demons[]

Arcturus (epic) by Polli, Vip3r, EyeOfTheStorm, Azasuh, Voltex, OlliKuu, FarDreamer, Tex02, and DiamondSplash. Cyber themed.

Betelgeuse (featured) by Cultrix, Nashii, L4mbads, Underpipse, Esecncia, Vyu, Kakemancool, Yoonsr, Slendy, BlasterRobotz, Elvii, LightVoid, Straw, Balloons, Helpegasus, Parallax, Belonzik, Nidro, SparkOmega, MinusX, Sepia, and Splash. It has a toxic/radioactive theme and was verified by EVW.

Polaris (epic) by Fofii, Zapper, FunnyGame, Zoroa GD, hfcRed, flashmick72, Belonzik, Voltex, Buragoz, Sepia, Enixy, Sley, Maxie25 and Splash.

Scorpius (epic) - A mega-collaboration with a jungle/fire theme and made by Reunomi, Oc3andark, Nashii, Miguel135, EnZore, Expy, Xender Game, BlowMyPooh, Cybronaut, Sepia, Escetity, and Splash. It was verified by Viprin.

Insane Demons[]

Acropolaris (featured) by Maxie25, Sepia, Belonzik, Enixy, Voltex, Splash, and mix991.

Extreme Demons[]

Epsilon (featured) by ​​​​​Pennutoh, Cosmic, Juhou, Hyenaedon, Matterz, Vulcan, SQRL, Bianox, Failure444, SlimJim, Cybronaut, ManoMagician, LeoX, Lazuli, Balloons, SirHadoken, Drift, Tex02, DiamondSplash, Jozhii and LeoCreatorX. It is the official prequel to Omicron.

Omicron (epic) by Peton, CosmicSabre, Pocke, Parallax, Goose, BlasterRobotz, Polli, Elvii, Vyu, Esencia, Toasted, SparksOmega, Cirtrax, EyeOfTheStorm, HugoLA, Dominus, Helpegasus, Belonzik, Azasuh, Nvatium, Kakemancool, Zipixbox, Kadex, Zafkiel, Skele, Nashiiii, Osiris, Joojmiguel, Splash, genericqueso, Sepia, Sequex, Zipiks, Surv, and Nexus. It is the official sequel to Epsilon.
